    <title>Worked Example: While Loops - Counter</title>
    <xi:include href='./subgoals-loops.ptx' />
    <subsection>
    <p>You can watch this video or read through the content below it.</p>

    <video xml:id="video-loops-we1" youtube="adoRks8Htfw" width="auto"/>
    <p>Problem: Given the following code, what is the output?</p>
    <program language="java">
        <input>
int counter = 0;
int total = 0;

while (counter &lt; 50)
{
    if (counter % 5 == 0)
            total += counter;
    counter++;
 }

 System.out.println(total);
        </input>
    </program>
